sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant APIA as API A
  participant Entra as Entra ID
  participant APIB as API B

  User->>APIA: Call API A (delegated token, aud: API A)
  APIA->>Entra: OBO exchange (token for aud: API B)
  Entra-->>APIA: OBO token (aud: API B)
  APIA->>APIB: Call API B (OBO token)
